lines: Why, I've served Raya–O since she was a little girl no bigger than me, kupo! She has matured much since the Calamity. Her brother A–Ruhn, on the other hand...
Why, I'd give my pom and tail to stand before the illustrious A–Towa–Cant!
And yet now I stand before you─which as I've heard from Raya–O is the next best thing, kupo!
